videos.description: Cam Reddish tries to make a statement as he pounds down a powerful two-handed dunk on the first possession of the game for the Hawks.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Reddish takes flight for early slam vs. Mavs) 2021/02/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Reddish takes flight for early slam vs. Mavs

videos.description: Maxi Kleber drains a 3-pointer and Trae Young quickly comes down the court to answer by draining a 3-pointer of his own from the Mavericks logo.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Young answers Kleber 3 with a 3 from the logo) 2021/02/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young answers Kleber 3 with a 3 from the logo

videos.description: Trae Young pulls up to drain a 3-pointer and draws contact from Kristaps Porzingis on the closeout for a chance at a 4-point play.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Young draws foul on Porzingis for and-1 3) 2021/02/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young draws foul on Porzingis for and-1 3

videos.description: Trae Young drops a smooth dime to John Collins who rises up to smash down a two-handed dunk with authority by a Mavs defender.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Young's sweet dime sets up Collins for emphatic finish) 2021/02/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young's sweet dime sets up Collins for emphatic finish

videos.description: Luka Doncic drives and tosses a lob to Willie Cauley-Stein, who smashes down a two-handed dunk for the Mavericks.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Luka sets up Cauley-Stein with alley-oop) 2021/02/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Luka sets up Cauley-Stein with alley-oop

videos.description: Luka Doncic surprises himself as he puts up a wild shot that somehow, someway goes in on the baseline.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Luka surprises himself with wild shot that falls) 2021/02/10 ESHEET

videos.headline: Luka surprises himself with wild shot that falls
